getBound().notice: Returns the allowed symmetric bound for target allocation (e.g. +- 5%)

getDebtLimit().notice: The debt limit that the total debt of a strategy may not exceed.

getPerformanceFee().details: The strategist is paid in LP tokens, while the remainder of the profit stays in the vault.      Default performance fee is set to 5% of harvested profits.
getPerformanceFee().notice: Returns the fee charged on a strategy's generated profits.

getReserveFee().notice: Returns the percentage of the performance fee which is allocated to the vault reserve

getStrategistFee().notice: Returns the percentage of the performance fee that goes to the strategist.

getTargetAllocation().details: this is to reduce gas costs. Withdrawals first come from idle funds and can therefore      avoid unnecessary gas costs.
getTargetAllocation().notice: The target percentage of total underlying funds to be allocated towards a strategy.

getTotalUnderlying().notice: Computes the total underlying of the vault: idle funds + allocated funds - debt

harvest().details: Harvesting adds profits to the vault's balance and deducts fees.  No performance fees are charged on profit used to repay debt.
harvest().notice: Harvest profits from the vault's strategy.

initializeStrategy(address).details: Bypasses the time delay, but can only be called if strategy is not set already.

prepareTargetAllocation(uint256).notice: Prepare update of target allocation (with time delay enforced).

withdraw(uint256).details: If the specified amount exceeds idle funds, an amount of funds is withdrawn      from the strategy such that it will achieve a target allocation for after the      amount has been withdrawn.
withdraw(uint256).notice: Withdraws specified amount of underlying from vault.

withdrawAll().notice: Withdraws all funds from vault and strategy and transfer them to the pool.

withdrawAllFromStrategy().details: Harvests profits before withdrawing. Deactivates strategy after withdrawing.
withdrawAllFromStrategy().notice: Withdraws all funds from strategy to vault.
